extendedInfo.description: The Robert Wood Johnson Foundation Health & Society Scholars is pleased to bring the scholars of the program together with our National Advisory Committee members, training site directors and faculty, alumni, RWJF staff and esteemed guests at this annual event. This meeting will also serve as an introduction of our eleventh cohort who will be attending this event as part of their orientation. The Annual Program Meeting is an important step in fostering the development of our scholars to conduct innovative research and work with policy-makers on issues important to the health and well-being of all Americans, by allowing them to receive feedback from their colleagues across the program.Keywords : Health & Society Scholars, HSS 2013, HSS
